        Key milestones in the development and launch of our AI solution.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative wrap overflow-hidden md:p-10 h-full">
      <div
        class="border-2-2 absolute border-opacity-20 border-main-400 h-full border"
        style="left: 50%"
      ></div>

      <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
        <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>

        <div class="z-20 flex items-center order-1 bg-main-400  w-3 h-3 rounded-full">
          </div>
        <div class="order-1  bg-opacity-30 w-5/12 md:px-6 md:py-4">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold text-main-700 uppercase mb-1">
            BIRTH
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium mb-1">July, 2025</p>
          <h3 class="mb-3 font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-800">
            Sakura was born
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            The initial thought process and research on the market began, laying the groundwork for the project's vision.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm mt-3 flex items-center text-main-400 font-medium hover:text-main-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
            Read Insights &nbsp;
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full left-timeline">
        <div class="order-1 rounded-lg w-5/12 md:px-6 md:py-4">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold text-green-700 uppercase mb-1">
            CUSTOMER-FIRST
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium mb-1">September, 2025</p>
          <h3 class="mb-3 font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-800">
            Building the MVP and talking to customers
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-snug tracking-wide text-gray-700">
            Adopted a customer-first approach by having in-depth conversations with guys at Kuda, Paystack, Heirs, Mantrac, LandWey, and more.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm mt-3 flex items-center text-main-400 font-medium hover:text-main-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
            View Research Summary &nbsp;
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="z-20 flex items-center order-1 bg-green-500 shadow-xl w-3 h-3 rounded-full">
          </div>
        <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8 flex justify-between items-center w-full right-timeline">
        <div class="order-1 w-5/12"></div>
        <div class="z-20 flex items-center order-1 bg-orange-500 shadow-xl w-3 h-3 rounded-full">
          </div>
        <div class="order-1  w-5/12 md:px-6 md:py-4">
          <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-700 uppercase mb-1">
            JOB
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium mb-1">October, 2025</p>
          <h3 class="mb-3 font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-800">
            Landed our first Client
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-snug tracking-wide text-gray-700">
            We are currently building a stable version of Sakura while working closely with our first client to deliver optimal results and gather real-world feedback.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm mt-3 flex items-center text-main-400 font-medium hover:text-main-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
            Client Case Study &nbsp;
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


